commit.message:
Makefile.in (vmsdbgout.o): Depend on function.h.

	* Makefile.in (vmsdbgout.o): Depend on function.h.

	* vmsdbgout.c: Include function.h.

From-SVN: r55815

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@

+

+
+	* vmsdbgout.c: Include function.h.
+

 	* prefix.c (update_path): Don't strip single `.' path components
